Set or Change a Static Enable Password

Enable privilege EXEC Mode
Switch> enable

Enter configuration mode
Switch# configure terminal

Define a new password or change an existing password
Switch(config)# enable password <password>

Protecting Enable and Enable Secret Passwords with Encryption

Define a secret password that is saved with a nonreversible encryption method
Switch(config)# enable secret level 1 password <password>

Encrypts the password when the password is defiend or when configuration is written
Switch(config)# service password-encryption

Set username, privilege level and password for each user
Switch(config)# username <user> privilege 1 password <password>
